 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Frisk:

    When this Pokémon enters battle, 
  it reveals an opposing Pokémon's 
  held item to all participating 
  trainers.

  In a double battle, if one 
  opponent has an item, this Pokémon 
  will Frisk that Pokémon; if both 
  have an item, it will Frisk one 
  at random.

  Competitive:

    Raises Special Attack by two 
  stages upon having any stat lowered.

  Shadow-tag:

    While this Pokémon is in battle, 
  opposing Pokémon cannot flee 
  or switch out.

  Other Pokémon with this ability 
  are unaffected. Pokémon with 
  run away can still flee. Pokémon 
  can still switch out with the 
  use of a move or item.


 Location Areas:
   Unova route 5 area
   Unova route 16 area
